lt.viko.eif.final_project.service

Class MissionServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • lt.viko.eif.final_project.service.MissionServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MissionService

    @Path(value="missions")
 @Consumes(value="application/json")
 @Produces(value="application/json")
public class MissionServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements MissionService
    This class implements a RESTful web service, which allows the client to perform CRUD operations with a database through a mission DAO. This web service produces and consumes JSON documents.
    Author:
    Tomas Jokubauskas
